node.text:
Chilling at home on Sinful Sunday while gorging on some @alferogelato is the best thing ever. When you have 6 pints of awesome gelato, you know you’re in a good place. 🤤

Another best thing? It’s 96% fat free so it’s not that sinful after all! 🌚
.
I’ve been a huge fan of their dark chocolate since awhile ago & I’m super happy that @alferogelato has launched their new E-SHOP & they are having 15% off their orders from now til 31st April!
.
It’s a min. order of above $70 but to me that’s easy peasy since their gelato is soooo good. 🤤 I live really far away from their shop & it’s pretty inconvenient for me to get their gelato but with this new E-SHOP? JUST WHACK ONLY. 🤩
.
